#

Tropical Protein Smoothie Bowl

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinVegetarian

Cuisine:

AmericanHealthy

Course:

BreakfastSnack

Tags:

Smoothie BowlHealthyQuickTropical

Description

A refreshing and nutrient-packed smoothie bowl topped with tropical fruits, perfect for breakfast or a post-workout snack.

Ingredients

  • frozen banana: 1 medium
  • frozen mango: 1 cup
  • greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • almond milk: 1/2 cup
  • chia seeds: 1 tablespoon
  • honey (optional): 1 tablespoon
  • granola: 1/4 cup
  • sliced kiwi: 1 medium
  • coconut flakes: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh berries (strawberries/blueberries): 1/2 cup
